; Coverage test for filters.cc
; Tests posts_as_equity::report_subtotal with multiple commodities
; total.to_amount path when total is single-commodity
; amount.is_zero skip in create_post_from_amount
; The equity command forces the filter pipeline through posts_as_equity.

2024/01/15 Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage          10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash               $-1500.00

2024/01/20 Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage          5 GOOG @ $100.00
    Assets:Cash               $-500.00

test equity
2024/01/20 Opening Balances
    Assets:Brokerage                         10 AAPL
    Assets:Brokerage                          5 GOOG
    Assets:Cash                            $-2000.00
    Equity:Opening Balances                 $2000.00
    Equity:Opening Balances                 -10 AAPL
    Equity:Opening Balances                  -5 GOOG
end test
